# Chapter Reorder Suggestion — Narrative Pipeline

Add AI-powered chapter reordering suggestion between outline generation and rewrite in the Narrative pipeline.

## Flow

```
Step 1: Generate Outline
Step 1.5 [NEW]: AI suggests optimal chapter order → popup (Accept/Skip) + CSV
Step 2: Rewrite (using new order if accepted, renumbered)
...Steps 3-6 unchanged
```

## Proposed Changes

### Core Logic

#### [MODIFY] [rewriter.py](file:///f:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/core/rewriter.py)

Add `suggest_chapter_order()`:
- Input: list of chapters `[{filename, text}]`  
- Sends to AI: all chapter summaries + ask for optimal narrative flow order
- Returns: `{suggested_order: [{original_index, new_index, filename, reason_vi}], strategy_vi}`
- Also add `export_reorder_csv(output_dir, suggestion)` → saves CSV with columns: `STT mới | STT cũ | Tên chapter | Lý do`

