### UI

#### [MODIFY] [rewrite_tab.py](file:///f:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/ui/rewrite_tab.py)

**In [_run()](file:///f:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/ui/rewrite_tab.py#1604-1628) of `_do_narrative_pipeline`:**
- After Step 1 (outline), call `suggest_chapter_order()`
- Export CSV to output dir
- Emit signal → show popup on main thread
- Popup: simple list showing old→new order + 3 buttons: **Accept** | **Skip** | **Open Suggestion** (opens CSV)
- If accepted: reorder [checked](file:///f:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/ui/rewrite_tab.py#625-635) list + renumber chapters
- Continue with rewrite using new order

**New signal:** `reorder_ready = pyqtSignal(dict, str)` — (suggestion, csv_path)

**New popup method:** `_show_reorder_dialog(suggestion, csv_path)` → returns accept/skip

